        <item>
            <title>PS5 Pro 官方拆机解构内部设计，液态金属、新风扇设计令散热效果更好、更宁静</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/22/ps5-pro-teardown-2/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ps5-pro-teardown-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/22/ps5-pro-teardown-2/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 22 Apr 2025 11:43:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PlayStation 5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1304504</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sony 近日公开 PlayStation 5 Pro 的拆解细节，揭示这款高阶主机在散热设计上的重大改良，成功解决原版 PS5 存在的液态金属渗漏与过热问题。透过更大面积风扇、重设扇叶形状以及改良液态金属涂层，PS5 Pro 带来更稳定表现，为长时间游玩提供稳妥支援。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769663_fd23f813.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304510" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769663_fd23f813-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769663_fd23f813-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769663_fd23f813.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/eff5991706e1e62ff196.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304535" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/eff5991706e1e62ff196-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/eff5991706e1e62ff196-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/eff5991706e1e62ff196.jpg 1088w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Sony PlayStation.Blog 官方网志昨日（21 日）发表 PS5 Pro 主机拆解文章，展示了这部新主机针对原版 PS5 热管理不足的问题作出多方面强化，特别是防止液态金属冷却系统出现渗漏。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513021_7d721965.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304525" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513021_7d721965-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513021_7d721965-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513021_7d721965.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674082_f307c712.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304524" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674082_f307c712-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674082_f307c712-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674082_f307c712.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769583_46267cd0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304514" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769583_46267cd0-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769583_46267cd0-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769583_46267cd0.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>针对主机整体散热，PS5 Pro 配备比原版更大的风扇，并采用重新设计的扇叶，每片扇叶之间再加入更细小扇叶，进一步提升气流效率，同时保持低噪音输出。土田信也表示，游戏主机的散热设计必须平衡效能与静音，这与一般风扇设计哲学不同，Sony 特别在气流「安静」输出上下功夫，避免风扇噪音干扰玩家沉浸感。</p><div class="mceTemp"></div><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704509_9ceaf531.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304511" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704509_9ceaf531-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704509_9ceaf531-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704509_9ceaf531.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲对比之下 PS5 Pro 风扇（左）比起原版 PS5（右）体积更大</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704469_601c3dd8.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304512" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704469_601c3dd8-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704469_601c3dd8-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704469_601c3dd8.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲每片扇叶之间再加入更细小扇叶，进一步提升气流效率，同时保持低噪音输出。</p><p>主机外观方面，PS5 Pro 保留家族设计语言，并加入三条横向通风缝隙，这些被工程团队称为「叶片」的设计，不但美观，同时提升气流流通能力。后方排气口面积亦增大，配合底部与背部进气，提升整体散热效能。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513031_2d1629d6.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304513" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513031_2d1629d6-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513031_2d1629d6-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513031_2d1629d6.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>主机内部，PS5 Pro 主机板尺寸较前代稍大，因应新增电路设计需求，调整风扇位置与 I/O 端口排列，将 HDMI、LAN、USB 等接口位置上移，以配合更紧凑主机板结构。为减少电磁干扰，主机板金属屏蔽层以多颗螺丝固定，确保电磁波干扰控制在安全标准以下，防止影响其他电子设备运作。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272827.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1304526" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272827-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272827-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272827.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272833.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1304527" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272833-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272833-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272833.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲翻开保护金属片就可看到主机板</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512961_2815e14e.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304515" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512961_2815e14e-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512961_2815e14e-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512961_2815e14e.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>PS5 Pro 主机板采用更多层数，将讯号通道藏于内层，有效提升记忆体讯号传输速度。记忆体配置方面，PS5 Pro 采用 8 颗升级版 GDDR6 记忆体，负责游戏高效能渲染，并新增一颗 DDR5 记忆体，专门处理作业系统等低速任务，实现性能分流。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769613_85832efe.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304516" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769613_85832efe-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769613_85832efe-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769613_85832efe.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲图中红圈位置为新增的记忆体</p><p>PS5 Pro 内部结构经过重新设计，最引人注目的改动包括液态金属冷却区域新增细槽，令冷却效果更稳定。Sony 工程团队领导成员土田信也（Shinya Tsuchida）指出，这些细槽有助固定液态金属位置，防止在主机垂直摆放时流出。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674017_fe2353e1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304519" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674017_fe2353e1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674017_fe2353e1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674017_fe2353e1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456876270_f0a57d3e.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304518" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456876270_f0a57d3e-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456876270_f0a57d3e-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456876270_f0a57d3e.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>散热器部分，PS5 Pro 配备更多铜制热导管与铝制散热鳍片，鳍片分成两段式设计，贴合主机内部结构，进一步提升散热效率，应对高效能游戏负载。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512956_02cd0b9a.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304520" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512956_02cd0b9a-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512956_02cd0b9a-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512956_02cd0b9a.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>电源供应部分，PS5 Pro 采用比现有 PS5 输出高出 48 瓦的电源模组，尺寸亦相应增大，以应对主机更高的功耗需求。电源模组曲面设计与机身内部完美贴合，细节甚至刻有「Sony Interactive Entertainment」字样，确保安装方向无误。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769563_60f2b887.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304523" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769563_60f2b887-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769563_60f2b887-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769563_60f2b887.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>网络连接方面，PS5 Pro 搭载最新 Wi-Fi 7 模组，成为首批支援此规格的游戏主机，虽则当初标准尚未正式发布，Sony 工程团队依然提前完成测试认证，保证玩家未来数年享受高速稳定的无线连接。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674022_1d8b90aa.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304521" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674022_1d8b90aa-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674022_1d8b90aa-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674022_1d8b90aa.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>总结而言，PS5 Pro 虽在外观与核心硬件提升幅度有限，但透过散热与内部结构优化，成功解决原版 PS5 的散热隐患，为玩家带来更稳定游戏体验。对于重视性能稳定与长时间游戏的玩家，PS5 Pro 可算是一个值得考虑的升级选择。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/22/ps5-pro-teardown-2/game-channel/">PS5 Pro 官方拆机解构内部设计，液态金属、新风扇设计令散热效果更好、更宁静</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
